'''半音'''是[[音乐|音乐]]中的一个术语，即一個[[小二度|小二度]]，是最不[[協和與不協和|協和]]的一個音<ref>{{cite book | title = Sound: An Elementary Text-book for Schools and Colleges | first = John Walton | last = Capstick | publisher = Cambridge University Press | year = 1913 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=bwNJAAAAIAAJ&pg=PA227&dq=most+dissonant-interval+semitone+intitle:sound | access-date = 2019-10-25 | archive-date = 2020-08-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200819010537/https://books.google.com/books?id=bwNJAAAAIAAJ&pg=PA227&dq=most+dissonant-interval+semitone+intitle:sound | dead-url = no }}</ref>。
[[十二平均律|十二平均律]]乃按照比例將音高频率平均分成12份，每份是一個半音，例如C{{sharp}}比C高半音。這些半音全部相等。但在其他音樂體系中，半音未必全部相等。
